__NOTOC__

Windstille is a 2D action adventure game released under the [http://www.gnu.org/licenses/licenses.html#GPL GPL] and [http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.5/ Creative Commmons] license, which basically means you can modify and redistribute it as you like, as long as you others to do the same with your modifications.

We are still looking for new developers to join this project, have a look at the [[Jobs]] section to see if you might be able to help.

